# Sub-Task 4.7: Monitoring, Alerts & Deploy Pipeline

## PROMETHEUS ALERT RULES — `infrastructure/monitoring/prometheus-rules.yaml`

```yaml
groups:
  - name: flow-alerts
    interval: 30s
    rules:
      - alert: HighFlowErrorRate
        expr: |
          (sum(rate(flow_execution_errors[5m])) / sum(rate(flow_executions[5m]))) > 0.05
        for: 5m
        annotations:
          summary: "Flow error rate > 5%"

      - alert: FlowCostOverrun
        expr: increase(flow_cost_usd[1h]) > 1000
        for: 10m
        annotations:
          summary: "Hourly cost exceeded $1,000"

      - alert: LowShadowModeAgreement
        expr: shadow_mode_agreement_rate < 0.90
        for: 30m
        annotations:
          summary: "Shadow mode agreement rate < 90%"

      - alert: FlowExecutionLatencyHigh
        expr: histogram_quantile(0.95, flow_execution_latency_ms) > 5000
        for: 5m
        annotations:
          summary: "Flow p95 latency > 5 seconds"
```

## DEPLOY PIPELINE — `.github/workflows/deploy-flows.yml`

```yaml
name: Deploy Flows to Production
on:
  workflow_dispatch:
    inputs:
      flowId: { required: true }
      environment: { default: staging, type: choice, options: [staging, production] }

jobs:
  validate:
    runs-on: ubuntu-latest
    steps:
      - uses: actions/checkout@v4
      - name: Validate flow JSON
        run: jq empty flows/definitions/${{ github.event.inputs.flowId }}.json
      - name: Run quality gates
        run: |
          promptfoo eval -c flows/tests/promptfoo-config.yaml
          PASS=$(promptfoo view --json | jq .passRate)
          [ "$PASS" -ge 95 ] || exit 1

  deploy-staging:
    needs: validate
    environment: staging
    steps:
      - name: Deploy to Langflow staging
        run: |
          curl -X POST http://langflow-staging:7860/api/flows \
            -H "Authorization: Bearer ${{ secrets.LANGFLOW_API_KEY_STAGING }}" \
            -d @flows/definitions/${{ github.event.inputs.flowId }}.json

  deploy-production:
    needs: deploy-staging
    if: github.event.inputs.environment == 'production'
    environment: production
    steps:
      - name: Canary deploy (10% traffic)
        run: kubectl patch service orchestrator -p '{"spec":{"selector":{"version":"canary"}}}'
      - name: Monitor for 5 minutes
        run: sleep 300
      - name: Check canary success rate
        run: |
          RATE=$(curl http://metrics-server/success-rate?flow=${{ github.event.inputs.flowId }})
          [ "$RATE" -ge 98 ] || (kubectl rollout undo deployment/orchestrator && exit 1)
      - name: Complete rollout
        run: kubectl patch service orchestrator -p '{"spec":{"selector":{"version":"stable"}}}'
```

## KUBERNETES DEPLOYMENT — `infrastructure/kubernetes/orchestrator-deployment.yaml`

```yaml
apiVersion: apps/v1
kind: Deployment
metadata:
  name: orchestrator
spec:
  replicas: 3
  template:
    spec:
      containers:
        - name: orchestrator
          image: sentra/orchestrator:latest
          livenessProbe:
            httpGet: { path: /health, port: 3000 }
            initialDelaySeconds: 30
            periodSeconds: 10
          readinessProbe:
            httpGet: { path: /ready, port: 3000 }
            initialDelaySeconds: 10
            periodSeconds: 5
```

